title: Ascend
description: Shen Sheng has always been obedient and never once deviated from the life course set for him by others. Everything changes when Cheng Mu, a literature professor, comes into his life. By accident, he discovers the young professor’s secret. At the same time, the professor also finds out about Shen Sheng’s unique talent. Their lives will never be the same again. Ascend Chen Sheng 沈升
